    Scope and Contents
International Studies records (1983-) contains announcements, brochures, newsletters and minutes, memos, reports and working papers of the International Task Force. International Studies was a thematic activity and was part of the Innovative &amp; Experimental Studies Cluster until 1991 when it became a minor.  This minor provides students with an understanding of the complex and changing world and methods of analysis for studying countries, societies and cultures.  
  
